text: Marius Vasile Cozmiuc (born 7 September 1992) is a Romanian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. He married fellow Olympic rower Ionela-Livia Lehaci in 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
